<item>
            <title>[OAK-224] Allow the ContentRepositoryImpl to receive a CommitEditor in the constructor</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-224</link>
                <project id="12313221" key="OAK">Jackrabbit Oak</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Following &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-154&quot; title=&quot;Full text search index&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;OAK-154&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;OAK-154&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; WIP, I&apos;d like to tweak the ContentRepositoryImpl&apos;s constructor to receive a CommitEditor.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This will allow us to turn the Lucene dependency back to optional.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
